---
title: Spinach, Cheddar & Black Bean Quesadillas with Tomato Salsa & Yoghurt
description: All hail the king of toasted breads, the cheesiest and most noble of dinner options, the mighty quesadilla! Tonight, we’ve filled them with a delicious mix of nutritious ingredients and paired it with a fresh tomato and spring onion salsa.
